            . I received her in charge about half-past seven o'clock with the pelisse; she said she found it within a few yards of the house.</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182212040051"></xptr>The prisoner, in her defence, stated the prosecutrix used most shocking oaths, and that she found the pelisse at the corner of Baldwin's gardens.</p>
